  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Montenegro: Strengthening Commercial Mediation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) To provide capacity building activities for mediators and judges. 2) To raise public awareness on ADR and mediation mechanism, with a focus on Small and Medium Enterprises.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mediators and judges of the Mediation Center and the Judicial Training Center, and the business community.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to assist the Government of Montenegro with promoting and facilitating the use of commercial mediation on a national scale, with the goal of making the use of Alternative Dispute Resolution (ADR) a business norm in the country.</narrative>
  </description>
